data.title: Dodge Center, Minnesota Population 2024
data.text:
Poverty in Dodge Center

The race most likely to be in poverty in Dodge Center is Native , with 23.68% below the poverty level.

The race least likely to be in poverty in Dodge Center is White , with 5.05% below the poverty level.

The poverty rate among those that worked full-time for the past 12 months was 0.56% . Among those working part-time, it was 13.33% , and for those that did not work, the poverty rate was 7.19% .
